            </div>
            <div class="card-sm">
              <div class="card-sm-icon purple-bg">
                <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="white">
                  <path d="M19.35 10.04C18.67 6.59 15.64 4 12 4 9.11 4 6.6 5.64 5.35 8.04 2.34 8.36 0 10.91 0 14c0 3.31 2.69 6 6 6h13c2.76 0 5-2.24 5-5 0-2.64-2.05-4.78-4.65-4.96z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3>Built w/ Astro</h3>
              <p>Lightning-fast performance & UX</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Author Section -->
      <section class="section">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="section-header">
            <h2>
              <span class="accent-bar"></span>
              About the Author
            </h2>
            <p>Expert educator ensuring only the best courses make it to CoursesWyn</p>
          </div>
          <div class="author-card">
            <div class="author-avatar">
              <img src="/images/author.jpg" alt="Andrew Derek - Udemy Coupon Expert" loading="lazy" />
            </div>
